page.title: 19HOUSE TYPES-INTAKE/CANTLEY
page.content: This survey identifies parts of the block,using National Grid references. {GR 6004:}Here there are mainly semi- detached houses built since 1950.There are some short terraces and high rise blocks within a local authority estate {GR 6003:}This area contains semi - detached housing built since 1950. {GR 6002:}This square has semi-detached housing within a council estate around Cantley Park.There is a mixture of "high-class" detached and semi - detached housing in private estates in the rest of the area. {GR 6104:}This contains semi-detached houses in part of the N.C.B. estate. {GR 6103:}This has an isolated C19th century farm cottage. {GR 6102:}Here there is a mixture of semi-detached and short terrace housing within a local authority estate.
